{"tid":1570623,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【警世】休班POPO新拘捕戰術利用《101A拘捕令》！","createTime":"2019-09-15T07:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T07:25:51.000Z","uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b309e04aec8a79df684ecf88c48668721a0e39b8","tid":1570623,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"休班POPO 用 第221章 《刑事訴訟程序條例》101A拘捕令拘捕手足，之後將被拘捕人士交俾當更POPO，休班POPO自己無須用警務人員就可以拘捕手足！<br />\n<br />\n101A.<strong>作出逮捕時武力的使用等</strong><br />\n(1)<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，可使用就當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。</span><br />\n(2)普通法中關於何時為第(1)款所述任何目的而使用武力，即因該目的而屬正當地使用武力的規定，由第(1)款予以取代。"},{"pid":"f7d244ff29ca05ecf7c0bd49304703b17af81151","tid":1570623,"uid":34793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"用同樣emphasis counter atk點睇？"},{"pid":"9ff5a3e3a9f8d3a1e1f6a206803bca4582429782","tid":1570623,"uid":10905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"要坐一年以上既罪行先得wor"},{"pid":"0c993ba7259465db1cbd48d8b6144145bcb3c304","tid":1570623,"uid":51085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"信我<br />\n個班唔係popo<br />\n係黑社會捉完人再交比popo"},{"pid":"cb87e66dffeaa88a0c88c3fd5b843e625b3a22b1","tid":1570623,"uid":68111,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"咁可唔可以用返101黎拘捕冒警popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd1481f5e3ec51c574c9e8c7a34004d7bc86764","tid":1570623,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c993ba7259465db1cbd48d8b6144145bcb3c304","tid":1570623,"uid":51085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"信我<br />\n個班唔係popo<br />\n係黑社會捉完人再交比popo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15